wrapped.summary: You're a disciplined player who thrives on consistency and smart decision-making in the mid lane. Your 59% win rate speaks volumes about your game knowledge and ability to control the tempo of matches.

highlights.title: Master of the Mid Lane
highlights.description: You dominated the mid lane with 56 games, securing a 58.93% win rate while outputting consistent damage with smart positioning.
highlights.flavor: You didn't just play mid—you owned it. This is where your talents truly shine.
highlights.label: Mid Lane Dominance

highlights.title: Aurora's Rising Star
highlights.description: Aurora was your hidden gem with an 80% win rate across 5 games, boasting an impressive 7.29 KDA that showcased your mastery of the champion.
highlights.flavor: When you pick Aurora, the enemy team should be scared. An 80% win rate isn't luck—it's mastery.
highlights.label: 80% Win Rate Champion

highlights.title: Damage Dealer Supreme
highlights.description: You averaged 138,004 total damage per game with 29,812 to champions, maintaining a 4.47 KDA across all 91 games.
highlights.flavor: Your damage output was relentless and efficient. Every spell, every auto attack mattered.
highlights.label: Average Total Damage Per Game

highlights.title: Early Game Execution
highlights.description: You secured 5.73 takedowns in the first 10 minutes and landed 54.99 CS by the 10-minute mark, showing exceptional early game fundamentals.
highlights.flavor: You didn't just farm—you hunted. Your early game pressure set the tone for victory after victory.
highlights.label: Takedowns in First 10 Minutes

highlights.title: Pick Mastery
highlights.description: You executed 9.65 pick kills with allies per game, demonstrating expert vision control and rotational timing throughout the season.
highlights.flavor: You had a sixth sense for where the enemy would be. Coordinated picks were your specialty.
highlights.label: Pick Kills with Allies Per Game

main.name: Yone
main.insight: Your Yone is absolutely lethal with a 71% win rate, showcasing your mastery of this high-skill duelist and your ability to navigate teamfights.

playstyle.summary: You're a versatile mid-laner with exceptional mechanics and team coordination, balancing aggressive playmaking with consistent strategic decision-making.

memorable.clutchestComeback: Multiple games where you turned around deficit teamfights with well-placed crowd control (averaging 25.81 enemy champion immobilizations per game) and coordinated pick plays.

funFacts: You dodged an average of 41 skill shots per game—you didn't just avoid damage, you made enemies whiff their entire combos.
Morning grind paid off: 11 AM ET was your peak play time with 22 games, suggesting you're a sharp early-riser who dominates when you're fresh.
You went full support mode occasionally: 2 utility role games with a 67 vision score average and 68% kill participation shows you can flex when needed.
Aurora stole your heart in Season 2025: Despite playing 6 champions, Aurora's 80% win rate made her your most reliable companion on the Rift.

closing.message: You've established yourself as a reliable, intelligent mid-laner with the mechanics and game sense to compete at a high level. With your 59% win rate, strategic depth, and champion mastery, you're poised for an incredible 2025 season ahead!
